xfields]], [[Northampton]]\n|attendance=1,382\n|referee=[[Simon Hooper]]\n|stack=Y\n}}\n\n===Football League Trophy===\n{{Main|2014\u201315 Football League Trophy}}\n\n{{football box collapsible\n|date=2 September 2014\n|time=19:45\n|round=First Round\n|team1=[[Wycombe Wanderers F.C.|Wycombe Wanderers]]\n|score=0\u20131\n|report=[http://www.ccfc.co.uk/fixtures-results/match-report/index.aspx?matchid=3770769 Report]\n|result=W\n|team2=Coventry City\n|goals1=[[Daniel Rowe (footballer, born 1992)|Rowe]] {{yel|51}}\n|goals2=[[Josh McQuoid|McQuoid]] {{goal|66}}<br />[[Conor Thomas|Thomas]] {{yel|90+1}}\n|stadium=[[Adams Park]], [[High Wycombe]]\n|attendance=1,685 ''(520 Sky Blue Army)''\n|referee=[[Mick Russell]]\n|stack=yes\n}}\n{{football box collapsible\n|date=7 October 2014\n|time=19:45\n|round=Second Round\n|team1=Coventry City\n|score=3\u20131\n|report=[http://www.ccfc.co.uk/fixtures-results/match-report/index.aspx?matchid=3781454 Report]\n|result=W\n|team2=[[Exeter City F.C.|Exeter City]]\n|goals1=[[Aaron Phillips|Phillips]] {{yel|25}} {{goal|35||45+1}}<br />[[Josh McQuoid|McQuoid]] {{goal|59}}\n|goals2=[[Ollie Watkins|Watkins]] {{goal|86}}\n|stadium=[[Ricoh Arena]], [[Coventry]]\n|attendance=7,273 ''(486 away)''\n|referee=Andrew Madley\n|stack=\n}}\n{{football box collapsible\n|date=12 November 2014\n|time=19:45\n|round= Area Quarter-Final\n|team1=Coventry City\n|score=2\u20130\n|report=[https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/29910224 BBC Report]\n|result=W\n|team2=[[Plymouth Argyle F.C.|Plymouth Argyle]]\n|goals1=[[James Maddison|Maddison]] {{yel|26}}<br />[[Gary Madine|Madine]] {{goal|61}}<br />[[Adam Barton (footballer)|Barton]] {{yel|84}}<br />[[Frank Nouble|Nouble]] {{goal|85}}<br />[[Andy Webster (footballer, born 1982)|Webster]] {{yel|90}}\n|goals2=\n|stadium=[[Ricoh Arena]], [[Coventry]]\n|attendance=7,121\n|referee=James Adcock\n|stack=yes\n}}\n{{football box collapsible\n|date=10 December 2014\n|time=19:45\n|round=Area Semi-Final\n|team1=[[Bristol City 